<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.8">
<l>vāmaṉa ṉeṉmarakata vaṇṇaṉ ṟāmaraik kaṇṇiṉaṉ</l>
<l>kāmaṉaip payantā yeṉṟeṉṟuṉ kaḻalpāṭi yēpaṇintu</l>
<l>tūmaṉat taṉaṉāyp piṟavit tuḻati nīṅka veṉṉait</l>
<l>tīmaṉaṅ keṭuttā yuṉakkeṉ ceykēṉeṉ cirītaraṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who destroyed the evil in my mind  so that the sorrow of birth left [me],</l>
<l>I being of pure mind, humbling myself at your ankleted [feet],</l>
<l>saying [and] saying “Vāman, my emerald-coloured one, lotus-eyed one,</l>
<l>you who begot Kāma” – what can I do for you, my bearer of Śrī?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
